------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Compiling TypeScript sources through ngc
ERROR: projects/components/src/lib/components.module.ts(8,39): error TS2322: Type 'typeof AbstractComponent' is not assignable to type 'any[] | Type<any>'.
  Type 'typeof AbstractComponent' is not assignable to type 'Type<any>'.
    Cannot assign an abstract constructor type to a non-abstract constructor type.

An unhandled exception occurred: projects/components/src/lib/components.module.ts(8,39): error TS2322: Type 'typeof AbstractComponent' is not assignable to type 'any[] | Type<any>'.
  Type 'typeof AbstractComponent' is not assignable to type 'Type<any>'.
    Cannot assign an abstract constructor type to a non-abstract constructor type.


</code></pre>


